{
  "texts": [
    "The CHSPC dataset is a great resource for researchers and machine learning practitioners when building algorithms for identifying cardiac diseases using heart sound recordings.",
    "The contest consisted of two rounds.",
    "The proficiency of the participants' segmentation algorithm abilities was assessed during the initial round.",
    "In contrast, the subsequent round focused on evaluating the algorithm's effectiveness in accurately categorizing heart sounds as \"normal, \" \"murmur, \" \"extra heart sound, \" or \"artifact\" within a laboratory setting.",
    "To assess the efficacy of the novel methodology, only the outcomes derived from the initial segment of the experiment, encompassing both datasets, were considered for analysis."
  ]
}